definitions.definition: Any fish of the needlefish family Belonidae , with a long narrow body and needle-shaped jaws, especially the European species Belone belone .
Any North or Central American fish of the family Lepisosteidae .

main_definition: ( especially UK , Ireland ) Any fish of the needlefish family Belonidae , with a long narrow body and needle-shaped jaws, especially the European species Belone belone .
secondary_definitions: ( especially US , Canada ) Any North or Central American fish of the family Lepisosteidae .
